title: Ep 2659 - Wheres the Phone?
shortDesc: Gogi finally gets the Super X-100 mobile phone and shares his happiness with his friends. When Gogi opens the box, he finds a soap instead of the phone.

title: Ep 2660 - Gogi Comes To Senses
shortDesc: After getting duped by Montu, Gogi takes help from Tapu sena and decides to go to Police station. Tapu sena informs Inspector Chalu Pandey about what happened with Gogi. Will inspector Chalu Pandey help Tapu Sena? Stay tuned!

title: Ep 2661 - Jethalal in Trouble
shortDesc: The police are tracking Gogi's phone. Chalu Pandey has vowed not to eat anything unless he finds the phone. Jethalal learns that Nattu Kaka and Baga have bought a second-hand phone.

title: Ep 2662 - Jethalal in Jail
shortDesc: After the police picks up Jethalal and put him behind bars, Nattu and Baga are tensed for him and inform Taarak and ask him to come over as soon as possible. Jethalal meanwhile tries to explain it to the policemen that he doesn't do anything illegal.

title: Ep 2663 - Confusion All Over
shortDesc: Amongst the chaos caused in the police station becuaswe of Gogi's phone, Jethalal finds out that Tapu is the one who has filed the complaint against the stolen phone. After all the chaos is over, police release Jethalal.

title: Ep 2664 - Champaklal Fired Up
shortDesc: Post entering the police station for the sim card of Jethalal, they see Chalu Pandey talking to Champaklal and Champaklal finds out that all of them are in police station and he fires up on Jethalal about why are they there.

title: Ep 2665 - A Lesson Learned
shortDesc: Tapu Sena and Jethalal narrate their ordeal to Champaklal and Sodhi. Then, Chalu Pandey pays a visit to Gokuldham society along with Montu. Montu is rebuked for his behavior by his parents and he apologizes to the Gokuldham society members.

title: Ep 2666 - Tapu Senas Trip
shortDesc: As the Tapu Sena is prepared to go for their college trip, Bhide is worried about them, and advises about being careful where they are going and asks them to study more and enjoy less. What will happen next? Stay tuned!

title: Ep 2667 - When Life Gives You Lemons
shortDesc: Jethalal's life today is surrounded by lemons today. When he leaves for his shop he bumps into Babita and the lemons she is carrying falls down. When Jethalal reaches the shop, he slips on a lemon and falls down.

title: Ep 2669 - Roshan Argues Roshan
shortDesc: Jethalal suggests that Sodhi speak to Roshan about not being able to go and to make up for it, he will take her shopping once she is back. But when he approaches with the idea, it backfires. What will happen next? Stay tuned!

title: Ep 2670 - Dinner At Bhides House
shortDesc: After Sodhi had promised of having dinner at Bhide's house, Madhavi invited Jethalal and Champaklal as weill for dinner. At Sodhi's garage, Sodhi's friends pop up and invite him for a party. Sodhi is in a fix, where two friendships are at stake.

title: Ep 2680 - Dinner At Bhides House
shortDesc: After their lie is caught and they reach at Sodhi's friends place, firstly they send Jethalal, Taarak and Hathi inside first and then they barge in. Roshan is very angry with Sodhi and runs after him with a hockey stick. How will this scenario end?

title: Ep 2671 - Sodhi Is Stuck
shortDesc: The situation is worsening for Sodhi as his friendship is at stake where attending both the sides is important to him and he looks towards Jethalal for help. Will Sodhi come out of the situation with a solution? Stay tuned!

title: Ep 2672 - The Stomach Ache
shortDesc: Following Jethalal's advice, Sodhi is all set to pretend that he has a stomach ache so that he can miss the dinner at Bhide's house and go partying with his friends.

title: Ep 2673 - The Check-Up
shortDesc: Champaklal calls Dr. Hathi to treat Sodhi, who is complaining of stomach pain. Jethalal fears that a check-up by Dr. Hathi will reveal the truth. Dr. Hathi decides to take Sodhi to his clinic and find the cause of the pain.
